text:
It’s very good app to manage the Orbi Router & satellites. I just switched to Orbi from other manufacturer, and missing some key features;
1. There is no way to see data used by each device (it shows only total data).
2. Although there is option to pause data per device, but no feature to set the schedule for each device (I know there is Circle app for partial stuff with a subscription fee but why it can’t be done in this app)
